      • createMessage

        ModbusMessage createMessage(int functionCode)
        This method creates a #ModbusMessage instance from #functionCode. The returned value can be either an instance of ModbusRequest or ModbusResponse.
        Parameters:
        functionCode - a number representing a modbus function
        Returns:
        an instance of a specific ModbusMessage
        See Also:
        ModbusRequest, ModbusResponse, ModbusMessageFactory, ModbusResponseFactory
